00:45:57.314 --> 00:45:58.420
And they were like, yeah!

00:45:58.420 --> 00:46:01.200
I never saw so much
optimism and hope.

00:46:01.200 --> 00:46:06.030
So like I absolutely think
this is a solvable problem.

00:46:06.030 --> 00:46:07.260
But we have the wrong story.

00:46:07.260 --> 00:46:09.676
And until we change that story
we're going to kind of be--

00:46:09.676 --> 00:46:10.860
our options will be limited.

00:46:10.860 --> 00:46:11.980
So I thank you very much.

