what's called the hard step

00:47:35.760 --> 00:47:37.080
model by Brandon Carter.

00:47:37.080 --> 00:47:38.340
And that's in-- the
hard step model has now

00:47:38.340 --> 00:47:40.350
become you know actually
essential, because you

00:47:40.350 --> 00:47:42.130
could actually calculate
probabilities out of it.

00:47:42.130 --> 00:47:42.838
