hard step model is true.

00:48:45.240 --> 00:48:47.239
But it's the best one
that we have that actually

00:48:47.239 --> 00:48:49.830
gives us-- allows us to
do something or articulate

00:48:49.830 --> 00:48:51.260
something numerically.

